{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Space Station Adventure: No response from Mars!</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A Martian station is no longer transmitting! The Company sends an under-qualified, under-equipped technician to fix the problem. Will he carry the weight of the Super-Corporation's expectations alone?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>No\u00a0!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Play as the artificial intelligence of his personal computer and help him win the challenges that lie ahead!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Through several chapters filled with mini-games, develop the AI's personality, win the trust of your biological colleagues and guide them through this interactive adventure where your every decision can decide the fate of all!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This multiple-choice story offers many twists and turns to avoid or follow, each with a different plot and a different ending!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An immersive text game: experience the adventure through AI sensors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Numerous high-impact mini-games: failure sometimes opens new doors!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A non-linear story: there are many forks in your path, leading to a multitude of endings!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A wide range of development opportunities: will you become an indispensable application or a malicious AI? Will you overcome your biological colleagues' prejudices or betray their trust?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A human and poignant narrative experience!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gameplay</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Take decisions for the AI and give good advice to your human technician.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/ch_en.png?t=1735806805\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Interact with the environment or with technical elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/mg_en.png?t=1735806805\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Consult information in your database.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/data_en.png?t=1735806805\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Return to certain points in the story using Checkpoints to test other paths.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3181780/extras/cp_en.png?t=1735806805\" /></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>A wealth of content</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">7 endings to discover, each with a multitude of variations</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A story of over 100,000 words</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">36 achievements to unlock</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No microtransactions, pay once for the full game</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Replay the story many times to discover all its secrets</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Valuable advice?","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3181780/171301dba86a8fef9b03982a7ad6693ef895d0a0.jpg"},{"name":"We know what you did!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3181780/52937b6d556285f762